  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt</title>

    <para>
      <application>xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt</application> is a backend for
      <application>xdg-desktop-portal</application>, that is using the Qt
      library.
    </para>

    &lfs120_checked;

